"```sql\nSELECT AVG(set_count) AS annual_average_sets\nFROM (\n  SELECT COUNT(id) AS set_count\n  FROM sets\n  WHERE releaseDate BETWEEN '2012-01-01' AND '2015-12-31'\n  GROUP BY YEAR(releaseDate)\n) AS yearly_set_counts;\n```\n\nTo find the common language of the card, you can use the following SQL query:\n\n```sql\nSELECT language, COUNT(language) AS language_count\nFROM set_translations\nGROUP BY language\nORDER BY language_count DESC\nLIMIT 1;\n```\n\nThese queries separately calculate the annual average number of sets released between 2012 and 2015 and determine the most common language in the `set_translations` table."